Pushy 0.1 API

This is the API documentation for Pushy, a Java library for sending APNs (iOS and OS X) push notifications.

See:
          Description

Packages
com.relayrides.pushy.apns Contains classes and interfaces for interacting with the Apple Push Notification service (APNs).
com.relayrides.pushy.apns.util Contains classes for working with APNs tokens and payloads.

 

This is the API documentation for Pushy, a Java library for sending APNs (iOS and OS X) push notifications. Pushy is written by RelayRides. For a higher-level description of Pushy and its goals, please visit the main project page.
